{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":876,"text":"We're going to share\na lot of secrets today, you and I,"},{"time":3835,"text":"and in doing so, I hope that we can lift"},{"time":6315,"text":"some of the shame\nmany of us feel about sex."}]},{"cues":[{"time":10915,"text":"How many here have ever been\ncatcalled by a stranger?"},{"time":16075,"text":"Lots of women."},{"time":18521,"text":"For me, the time I remember best"},{"time":21202,"text":"is when that stranger\nwas a student of mine."},{"time":25595,"text":"He came up to me after class that night"},{"time":28555,"text":"and his words confirmed\nwhat I already knew:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":31435,"text":"\"I am so sorry, professor."},{"time":33235,"text":"If I had known it was you,\nI would never have said those things.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":37155,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":39475,"text":"I wasn't a person to him\nuntil I was his professor."},{"time":44515,"text":"This concept, called objectification,"},{"time":47115,"text":"is the foundation of sexism,"},{"time":49195,"text":"and we see it reinforced\nthrough every aspect of our lives."},{"time":55635,"text":"We see it in the government"},{"time":57875,"text":"that refuses to punish men"},{"time":61315,"text":"for raping women."},{"time":63075,"text":"We see it in advertisements."},{"time":65395,"text":"How many of you have seen an advertisement"},{"time":67427,"text":"that uses a woman's breast\nto sell an entirely unrelated product?"},{"time":74515,"text":"Or movie after movie after movie"},{"time":78315,"text":"that portrays women\nas only love interests?"},{"time":82195,"text":"These examples might seem\ninconsequential and harmless,"},{"time":85835,"text":"but they're insidious,"},{"time":87115,"text":"slowly building into a culture\nthat refuses to see women as people."},{"time":91955,"text":"We see this in the school\nthat sends home a 10-year-old girl"},{"time":96169,"text":"because her clothes were\na distraction to boys trying to learn,"},{"time":99835,"text":"or the government that refuses\nto punish men for raping women"},{"time":105035,"text":"over and over,"},{"time":106635,"text":"or the woman who is killed"},{"time":108115,"text":"because she asked a man to stop\ngrinding on her on the dance floor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115515,"text":"Media plays a large role in perpetuating\nthe objectification of women."},{"time":121395,"text":"Let's consider\nthe classic romantic comedy."},{"time":124235,"text":"We're typically introduced\nto two kinds of women in these movies,"},{"time":128155,"text":"two kinds of desirable women, anyway."},{"time":130915,"text":"The first is the sexy bombshell."},{"time":133355,"text":"This is the unbelievably gorgeous woman\nwith the perfect body."},{"time":137035,"text":"Our leading man\nhas no trouble identifying her"},{"time":139675,"text":"and even less trouble having sex with her."},{"time":142755,"text":"The second is our leading lady,"},{"time":144635,"text":"the beautiful but demure woman\nour leading man falls in love with"},{"time":148515,"text":"despite not noticing her at first"},{"time":150675,"text":"or not liking her if he did."},{"time":153835,"text":"The first is the slut."},{"time":155875,"text":"She is to be consumed and forgotten."},{"time":157915,"text":"She is much too available."},{"time":159795,"text":"The second is desirable but modest,"},{"time":163475,"text":"and therefore worthy\nof our leading man's future babies."},{"time":166955,"text":"Marriage material."},{"time":168755,"text":"We're actually told\nthat women have two roles,"},{"time":171715,"text":"but these two roles have a difficult time\nexisting within the same woman."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176555,"text":"On the rare occasion\nthat I share with a new acquaintance"},{"time":180235,"text":"that I study sex,"},{"time":181995,"text":"if they don't end\nthe conversation right then,"},{"time":184395,"text":"they're usually pretty intrigued."}]},{"cues":[{"time":187315,"text":"\"Oh. Tell me more.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":189115,"text":"So I do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192195,"text":"\"I'm really interested\nin studying the sexual behaviors"},{"time":194835,"text":"of pregnant and postpartum couples.\""},{"time":196635,"text":"At this point I get\na different kind of response."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200195,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":202195,"text":"\"Oh. Huh."},{"time":204675,"text":"Do pregnant people even have sex?"},{"time":208075,"text":"Have you thought\nabout studying sexual desire"},{"time":212035,"text":"or orgasms?"},{"time":213395,"text":"That would be interesting, and sexy.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":218115,"text":"Tell me. What are the first words\nthat come to mind"},{"time":220675,"text":"when you picture a pregnant woman?"},{"time":223275,"text":"I asked this question\nin a survey of over 500 adults,"},{"time":226715,"text":"and most responded with \"belly\" or \"round\""},{"time":230315,"text":"and \"cute.\""},{"time":233035,"text":"This didn't surprise me too much."},{"time":234675,"text":"What else do we label as cute?"},{"time":237835,"text":"Babies. Puppies. Kittens."},{"time":240355,"text":"The elderly. Right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":242035,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":245050,"text":"When we label an adult as cute, though,"},{"time":247731,"text":"we take away a lot of their intelligence,"},{"time":250235,"text":"their complexity."},{"time":252195,"text":"We reduce them to childlike qualities."},{"time":255555,"text":"I also asked heterosexual men"},{"time":257235,"text":"to imagine a woman that they're\npartnered with is pregnant,"},{"time":260395,"text":"and then asked women\nto imagine that they are pregnant,"},{"time":263195,"text":"and then tell me\nthe first words that come to mind"},{"time":265835,"text":"when they imagine having sex."},{"time":268955,"text":"Most of the responses were negative."},{"time":272242,"text":"\"Gross.\""},{"time":273693,"text":"\"Awkward.\""},{"time":275090,"text":"\"Not sexy.\" \"Odd.\""},{"time":277555,"text":"\"Uncomfortable.\""},{"time":279235,"text":"\"How?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":280515,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":283315,"text":"\"Not worth the trouble.\"\n\"Not worth the risk.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":286435,"text":"That last one really stuck with me."},{"time":289715,"text":"We might think that because we divorce\npregnant women and moms from sexuality,"},{"time":294475,"text":"we are removing the constraints\nof sexual objectification."},{"time":299515,"text":"They experience less sexism. Right?"},{"time":302235,"text":"Not exactly."},{"time":303835,"text":"What happens instead\nis a different kind of objectification."},{"time":307755,"text":"In my efforts to explain this to others,"},{"time":310035,"text":"one conversation\nled to the Venus of Willendorf,"},{"time":313835,"text":"a Paleolithic figurine scholars assumed\nwas a goddess of love and beauty,"},{"time":318675,"text":"hence the name Venus."},{"time":320515,"text":"This theory was later revised, though,"},{"time":322675,"text":"when scholars noted\nthe sculptor's obvious focus"},{"time":326395,"text":"on the figurine's reproductive features:"},{"time":329835,"text":"large breasts,\nconsidered ideal for nursing;"},{"time":333115,"text":"a round, possibly pregnant belly;"},{"time":335755,"text":"the remnants of red dye,\nalluding to menstruation or birth."},{"time":340555,"text":"They also assumed that she was\nmeant to be held or placed lying down"},{"time":344114,"text":"because her tiny feet\ndon't allow her to be freestanding."},{"time":348515,"text":"She also had no face."},{"time":350795,"text":"For this reason, it was assumed\nthat she was a representation of fertility"},{"time":354915,"text":"and not a portrait of a person."},{"time":357795,"text":"She was an object."},{"time":359675,"text":"In the history of her interpretation,"},{"time":361515,"text":"she went from object\nof ideal beauty and love"},{"time":364675,"text":"to object of reproduction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":367355,"text":"I think this transition speaks more"},{"time":369835,"text":"about the scholars\nwho have interpreted her purpose"},{"time":373635,"text":"than the actual purpose\nof the figurine herself."},{"time":378355,"text":"When a woman becomes pregnant,"},{"time":380475,"text":"she leaves the realm\nof men's sexual desire"},{"time":384235,"text":"and slides into her reproductive\nand child-rearing role."},{"time":388835,"text":"In doing so, she also becomes"},{"time":391475,"text":"the property of the community,"},{"time":393275,"text":"considered very important\nbut only because she's pregnant. Right?"},{"time":398315,"text":"I've taken to calling this\nthe Willendorf effect,"},{"time":400835,"text":"and once again we see it reinforced\nin many aspects of her life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":405218,"text":"Has anyone here\never been visibly pregnant?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":407755,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":408995,"text":"Yeah. Lots of you, right?"},{"time":410275,"text":"So how many of you ever had a stranger\ntouch your belly during pregnancy,"},{"time":414435,"text":"maybe without even asking\nyour permission first?"},{"time":417795,"text":"Or told what you can and cannot eat"},{"time":420555,"text":"by somebody who is not your doctor,\nyour medical care provider?"},{"time":424195,"text":"Or asked private questions\nabout your birth plan?"},{"time":428075,"text":"And then told why\nthose choices are all wrong?"},{"time":431555,"text":"Yeah, me too."},{"time":432795,"text":"Or had a server refuse\nto bring you a glass of wine?"},{"time":437075,"text":"This one might give you pause,\nI know, but stay with me."},{"time":439835,"text":"This is a huge secret."},{"time":441955,"text":"It is actually safe to drink\nin moderation during pregnancy."},{"time":446515,"text":"Many of us don't know this"},{"time":448075,"text":"because doctors don't trust\npregnant women with this secret --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":451835,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":457355,"text":"especially if she's less educated\nor a woman of color."}]},{"cues":[{"time":461635,"text":"What this tells us is,"},{"time":463395,"text":"this Willendorf effect,\nit's also classist and racist."},{"time":467635,"text":"It's present when\nthe government reminds women"},{"time":473555,"text":"with every new anti-choice bill"},{"time":476235,"text":"that the contents of her uterus\nare not her own,"},{"time":479115,"text":"or when an ob-gyn says,"},{"time":481195,"text":"\"While it's safe\nto have sex during pregnancy,"},{"time":483515,"text":"sometimes you never know."},{"time":484875,"text":"Better safe than sorry, right?\""},{"time":487395,"text":"She's denied basic privacy\nand bodily autonomy"},{"time":491675,"text":"under the guise of \"be a good mother.\""},{"time":494155,"text":"We don't trust her\nto make her own decisions."},{"time":497115,"text":"She's cute, remember?"},{"time":501795,"text":"When we tell women"},{"time":504115,"text":"that sexual pleasure -- excuse me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":507075,"text":"When we tell women that sex\nisn't worth the risk during pregnancy,"},{"time":511915,"text":"what we're telling her is that\nher sexual pleasure doesn't matter."},{"time":516195,"text":"So what we are telling her\nis that she in fact doesn't matter,"},{"time":519515,"text":"even though the needs of her fetus\nare not at odds with her own needs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":525195,"text":"So medical providers,"},{"time":527475,"text":"such as the American College\nof Obstetricians and Gynecologists"},{"time":530475,"text":"have the opportunity to educate\nabout the safety of sex during pregnancy."},{"time":535395,"text":"So what do the experts say?"},{"time":537755,"text":"ACOG actually has\nno public official statement"},{"time":540275,"text":"about the safety of sex during pregnancy."},{"time":544078,"text":"Guidance from the Mayo Clinic\nis generally positive"},{"time":547115,"text":"but presented with a caveat:"},{"time":549635,"text":"\"Although most women can safely\nhave sex throughout pregnancy,"},{"time":552810,"text":"sometimes it's best to be cautious.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":554955,"text":"Some women don't want\nto have sex during pregnancy,"},{"time":558075,"text":"and that's OK."},{"time":559355,"text":"Some women do want\nto have sex during pregnancy,"},{"time":561995,"text":"and that's OK, too."},{"time":563435,"text":"What needs to stop\nis society telling women"},{"time":566115,"text":"what they can and cannot do\nwith their bodies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":569475,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":576035,"text":"Pregnant women are not faceless,\nidentity-less vessels of reproduction"},{"time":580715,"text":"who can't stand on their own two feet."},{"time":584115,"text":"But the truth is, the real secret is,"},{"time":586555,"text":"we tell all women that\ntheir sexual pleasure doesn't matter."},{"time":590835,"text":"We refuse to even acknowledge\nthat women who have sex with women"},{"time":594075,"text":"or women who don't\nwant children even exist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":596835,"text":"\"Oh, it's just a phase ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":598555,"text":"she just needs the right man\nto come along.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":602155,"text":"Every time a woman has sex"},{"time":604515,"text":"simply because it feels good,"},{"time":606515,"text":"it is revolutionary."},{"time":608275,"text":"She is revolutionary."},{"time":610475,"text":"She is pushing back\nagainst society's insistence"},{"time":613075,"text":"that she exist simply for men's pleasure"},{"time":615315,"text":"or for reproduction."},{"time":618435,"text":"A woman who prioritizes\nher sexual needs is scary,"},{"time":622435,"text":"because a woman who prioritizes\nher sexual needs prioritizes herself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":627595,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":631395,"text":"That is a woman demanding\nthat she be treated as an equal."},{"time":635835,"text":"That is a woman who insists"},{"time":637395,"text":"that you make room for her\nat the table of power,"},{"time":640755,"text":"and that is the most terrifying of all"},{"time":642675,"text":"because we can't make room for her"},{"time":645515,"text":"without some of us giving up\nthe extra space we hold."}]},{"cues":[{"time":650835,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":656475,"text":"I have one last secret for you."},{"time":658955,"text":"I am the mother of two boys"},{"time":660835,"text":"and we could use your help."},{"time":663315,"text":"Even though my boys hear me say regularly"},{"time":668035,"text":"that it's important for men\nto recognize women as equals"},{"time":671595,"text":"and they see their father modeling this,"},{"time":674155,"text":"we need what happens in the world\nto reinforce what happens in our home."},{"time":678595,"text":"This is not a men's problem\nor a women's problem."},{"time":681915,"text":"This is everyone's problem,"},{"time":683515,"text":"and we all play a role\nin dismantling systems of inequality."},{"time":688515,"text":"For starters, we have got\nto stop telling women"},{"time":691155,"text":"what they can and cannot do\nwith their bodies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":693595,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":698235,"text":"This includes not treating pregnant women\nlike community property."},{"time":702155,"text":"If you don't know her,\ndon't even ask to touch her belly."},{"time":705875,"text":"You wouldn't anybody else."},{"time":707595,"text":"Don't tell her\nwhat she can and cannot eat."},{"time":709755,"text":"Don't ask her private details\nabout her medical decisions."},{"time":712795,"text":"This also includes understanding"},{"time":714715,"text":"that even if you are\npersonally against abortion,"},{"time":717315,"text":"you can still fight\nfor a woman's right to choose."},{"time":720515,"text":"When it comes to women's equality,\nthe two need not oppose one another."},{"time":724995,"text":"If you're somebody who has sex with women,"},{"time":727275,"text":"prioritize her pleasure."},{"time":728795,"text":"If you don't know how, ask."},{"time":732075,"text":"If you have children --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":733595,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":735555,"text":"have conversations about sex\nas early as possible,"},{"time":739355,"text":"because kids don't look up s-e-x\nin the dictionary anymore."},{"time":743755,"text":"They look it up on the internet."},{"time":746355,"text":"And when you're having\nthose conversations about sex,"},{"time":749795,"text":"don't center them on reproduction only."},{"time":751755,"text":"People have sex for many reasons,"},{"time":753435,"text":"some because they want a baby,"},{"time":755235,"text":"but most of us have sex\nbecause it feels good."},{"time":758195,"text":"Admit it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":760795,"text":"And regardless of whether\nyou have children or not,"},{"time":763395,"text":"support comprehensive sex education\nthat doesn't shame our teenagers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":767675,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":776155,"text":"Nothing positive comes from shaming teens"},{"time":778755,"text":"for their sexual desires, behaviors,"},{"time":782155,"text":"other than positive STD\nand pregnancy tests."}]},{"cues":[{"time":786635,"text":"Every single day,\nwe are all given the opportunity"},{"time":789715,"text":"to disrupt patterns of inequality."},{"time":792995,"text":"I think we can all agree\nthat it's worth the trouble to do so."}]},{"cues":[{"time":797235,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":798475,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}